---
---
<section class="quote">
  <div class="wrap quote__wrap">
    <div class="eyebrow-row reveal"><span class="tick"></span> Filosofia</div>
    <h2 class="quote__h reveal reveal--lag-1">
      Tu dinero no necesita<br />gr&aacute;ficos sofisticados.<br />
      Necesita que <span class="stamp"><span class="inner">SEPAS</span></span><br />a d&oacute;nde se va.
    </h2>
    <div class="quote__rule reveal reveal--lag-2"></div>
    <div class="quote__attrib reveal reveal--lag-2">&mdash; Equipo INOUT &middot; en construccion, 2026</div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .quote {
    padding-top: clamp(96px, 12vw, 160px);
    padding-bottom: clamp(96px, 12vw, 160px);
    text-align: left;
  }
  .quote__wrap { max-width: 1100px; }
  .quote__h {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 6.5vw, 96px);
    line-height: 0.96;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin: 22px 0 0;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
  .quote__h .stamp {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0 0.18em;
    background: var(--color-green);
    transform: skewX(-6deg);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .quote__h .stamp .inner {
    display: inline-block;
    transform: skewX(6deg);
  }
  .quote__rule {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--color-ink);
    width: 84px;
    margin: 36px 0 24px;
  }
  .quote__attrib {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-ink-60);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
</style>
